HEADWORD: Bos
<hw>Bos</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>prop. n.</pos> <ety>[L., ox,
cow.]</ety> <fld>(Zool.)</fld> <def>A genus of ruminant quadrupeds,
